            <title>假冒八達通公司騙案激增，上週 71 人報警 + 警方舉出重要案例提醒市民</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/last-week-71-people-called-the-police-in-connection-with-the-octopus-phishing-scam/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=last-week-71-people-called-the-police-in-connection-with-the-octopus-phishing-scam</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/last-week-71-people-called-the-police-in-connection-with-the-octopus-phishing-scam/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蔣納偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 06:12:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[八達通]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[騙案]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1206992</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科在其 Facebook 專頁「守網者」發出警告，指出上週假冒八達通的釣魚騙案急劇上升。在短短一週內，已有至少 71 人報案，涉及的總損失超過 21 萬港元。這些騙案的手法以八達通積分為誘餌，通過 SMS 短訊發送假連結，詐取受害者的個人和金融資料。</p><p>警方發帖文詳細説明，騙徒通過發送 SMS 短訊，聲稱八達通積分即將到期，引誘公眾點擊連結，進入一個偽冒的八達通網站。在這些網站上，受害者被要求輸入電話號碼、驗證碼和八達通號碼等資料，從而使騙徒能夠登入其電子錢包並轉走資產。部分假網站甚至要求輸入信用卡資料、安全代碼（CVV）和一次性密碼等，進行未經授權的交易。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n.jpg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>此外，警方還發現了一款名為「八達通（內測）」的疑似有毒應用程式。經過初步分析，該應用程式被認為能夠獲取 Android 用戶的手機存取權限，從而進行非法行為。警方提醒市民，切勿隨意點擊不明連結，不要輕易透露個人或敏感資料。市民應從官方渠道下載應用程式，並使用防毒軟件，保持系統及應用程式的最新更新，以防範此類網絡攻擊。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n.jpg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>警方表示，如果遇到可疑個案，市民可以進入<a href="https://cyberdefender.hk/?fbclid=IwAR3jw8bnim9mJLAHdUeXNxdHIPYhwnbwgjQcdKV0z2avqtwztdeMduUaFfM">守網者網站</a>用「防騙視伏器」或手機版「防騙視伏 App」，輸入有關網址、社交帳戶、電話號碼，收款賬號等，即時評估詐騙風險</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCyberDefenderHK%2Fposts%2F377230067991008&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="549" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>資料來源：Facebook</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

